text: The four-stroke engine is an internal combustion engine. The four strokes are: Stroke Alias Piston Intake valve Exhaust valve intake suck opens, sucks in air + fuel open closed compression squeeze closes, compressing the air + fuel closed closed combustion bang opens, because air + fuel combust, expanding gas in cylinder closed closed exhaust blow closes, blowing out the used gasses closed open ==Related pages== * Two-stroke engine Category:Motors
